g.title: AWS CloudFormation Sample Template WorkerRole: Create a multi-az, Auto Scaled worker that pulls command messages from a queue and execs the command. Each message contains a command/script to run, an input file location and an output location for the results. The application is Auto-Scaled based on the amount of work in the queue. **WARNING** This template creates one or more Amazon EC2 instances and an Amazon SQS queue. You will be billed for the AWS resources used if you create a stack from this template.
